        It also helps if we teach about or create a post on the concept, so that it remains clear.<br/>
        Here I’m writing <a target="_blank" href="/posts/">posts</a> about the various topics that I have learned over time.
        Also sharing my <a target="_blank" href="/studies/">studies</a>, which helps in the easy lookup of concepts/commands.<br />
