        I created this site years back in 2015.
        After having seen and worked on numerous websites, it was a wish to create a website on my own and deploy it in production.
        Actually it helped me in many ways:
        <ul>
            <li>To learn the DevOps aspect of websites. Domain name purchase, Hosting, Webservers, NameServers etc</li>
            <li>Brand of my own, where I can post my learnings and findings</li>
            <li>As a project that I can use to migrate between different technologies and in turn learn that technology</li>
        </ul>
        Of late, I don't do much updates to this site. I mostly publish my updates to <a href="https://github.com/bnyjohns" target="_blank">GitHub</a> which I find much easier to maintain.
